                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-528088145" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="528088145">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dfich/">一页书</a>
                    <span>2012-05-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">言者不如知者默，此语我闻于老君。若道老君是知者，缘何自著五千言。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="424376960">
